  "description": "Group envelope rate cranked high — voices cycling through peak amplitude at 3 Hz creates a tremolo-like shimmer when all notes are held. The filter resonance is pushed to 0.55 to add a bright ringing overtone on every group crest. Prismatic because no two chords refract identically.",
